q.p:
It has arisen; destroy it, destroy! Jvālājihvā, destroy it, destroy!
   Wherever it has arisen—destroy it, destroy—there you should go—destroy
   it, destroy! Svāhā! {5}

lg.l:
    Oṃ, Śravaṇapiśācī,
Muṇḍā, svāhā!
{10}

